Curlew Multimedia Converter:
----------------------------

Description:
------------

Easy to use and Free Multimedia converter for Linux.


Requirements:
-------------

- python-gobject >= 3.0
- ffmpeg
- mencoder
- xdg-utils
- libavcodec-extra-53 (recommended)



License:
--------

Waqf public license.
Please see LICENSE-ar.txt/LICENSE-en files for more informations.


Installation:
-------------

Run script "install" as root. (ex: sudo ./install).


Remove:
-------

Run script "uninstall" as root. (ex: sudo ./uninstall).

